{"tid":1456742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返唔返去機場？","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:02:09.000Z","uid":120308,"like":36,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"10c438e299caa0d2a3a0d2be0d7e86179d74d9f0","tid":1456742,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"首先對唔住先，我都比大量訊息左右左走定唔走。<br />\n而家既然已經確定左好多都係fake news，究竟入唔入返去？<br />\n我唸好多人都未走得好遠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重返<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />他日再回"},{"pid":"efd1e0f1baa1b21a17e9fbde83245ac8d1eeb929","tid":1456742,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b946f63d12d5961cfd5c436513c3b5652c6c46c5","tid":1456742,"uid":197393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"返"},{"pid":"23b9ad354e1062402bb9b041abeabdac4e9560e5","tid":1456742,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"離港航班已經全部cancel哂。<br />\n你睇抵港時間，無錯9點幾都仲有飛機降落，但係咁多示威者走唔走得切呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果去到9點幾都仲有好多人，到時一定走唔切。<br />\n<br />\n機場而家咁多人，等最後一班機嚟旅客出埋嚟先走，一定大把人走唔切。"},{"pid":"765c99ac0cd7a9934169fa0a119b0566a64101c9","tid":1456742,"uid":120308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:45:44.000Z","msg":"我都唔知返唔返好，無人返去一定送頭，要返就一齊返"},{"pid":"a6a5fdf4eec8760dd2971228f3f049059ca2f5fb","tid":1456742,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:47:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"214c1cc98f0356fa92ac26139cf78e62b1f5280a","tid":1456742,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bd4e2099b251ce8692d86975b23e60ab03bc4ba0","tid":1456742,"uid":131999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"番 我放工好多同事去緊"},{"pid":"cf438864b3ca1